body:
So yeah, my client starts up extremely slowly.{{summoner:3}} 
Yes, I have a high-end pc so it's not for that.{{summoner:4}} 
My patcher opens up normally, and when I click launch, it opens normally too.
Everything is normal until I login.
When I have logged in, it takes from 30 seconds to 2 minutes before I can click on anything, my profile, friends lists etc.
Also the tabs which show the featured skins etc. load up extremely slow. When the lag is gone, everything is fine, this is just annoying as hell.

I will greatly appreciate any support you guys could give me.{{summoner:7}} 

Thank you in advance!
